    <div class="container md:w-4/5 mx-auto px-4 py-6 md:pb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-center md:text-4xl font-bold pb-2">Our 100% Donation Model</h2>
        <p class="pb-4">
            Meals for the NHS uniquely runs a 100% model. All donations go only to direct costs for meals for NHS staff &mdash; that&rsquo;s food, delivery and payments processing for website donations.
        </p>
